  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_17931-18001",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "17931-18001",
      "markText": "“一个领导，”他说，“就像一个牧羊人。他站在羊群后面，让最敏捷、最聪明的羊走在前面，而其它羊则紧随其后。不要指望从羊群后面对它们发号施令。”",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17931&rangeEnd=18001",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17931&rangeEnd=18001"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_5478-5527",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5478-5527",
      "markText": "我们总是盼着自由来临的时候，将迎来光辉岁月，其实光辉岁月并非只在将来，更在我们承受并拒绝苦难之时。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5478&rangeEnd=5527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5478&rangeEnd=5527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_1282-1357",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1282-1357",
      "markText": "对于这样一个人物，了解他的优点远比缺点更重要，因为他的某些缺点已广泛地存在于同时代人物当中，而他在完成天命时所具有的良知、勇气在同时代却是屈指可数的。",
      "totalCount": 350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1282&rangeEnd=1357",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1282&rangeEnd=1357"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_1151-1228",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1151-1228",
      "markText": "或许每个人都有自己的天命，只是有的人并不知道自己有何天命，或虽知其天命，大多又都辜负了自己的天命。就后者而言，他们不是死在人生的结尾，而是死在人生的中途。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1151&rangeEnd=1228",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1151&rangeEnd=1228"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_9_11006-11043",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "11006-11043",
      "markText": "学位本身并不是晋升的保证，只有走出大学、融入社会中证明自己，学位才有价值。",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11006&rangeEnd=11043",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11006&rangeEnd=11043"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_3_1141-1187",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1141-1187",
      "markText": "我们希望保持一种非功利的兴趣：对世界的丰富性、复杂性本身充满兴趣，真诚地渴望理解他人的经验。",
      "totalCount": 276,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1141&rangeEnd=1187",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1141&rangeEnd=1187"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_28017-28089",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "28017-28089",
      "markText": "我很快认识到，我必须以自己的能力而不是凭借血统开辟自己的道路。我的同学多数在运动场上超过我，在课堂上思维也比我敏捷，我还有很多东西需要奋起直追。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=28017&rangeEnd=28089",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=28017&rangeEnd=28089"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_4887-4983",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4887-4983",
      "markText": "当我躺在床上，行将就木时，我突然意识到：如果一开始我仅仅去改变我自己，然后作为一个榜样，我可能改变我的家庭；在家人的帮助和鼓励下，我可能为国家做一些事情。然后谁知道呢？我甚至可能改变这个世界。",
      "totalCount": 264,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4887&rangeEnd=4983",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4887&rangeEnd=4983"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_3418-3484",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3418-3484",
      "markText": "历史上任何直接针对人性的改造都以失败告终，真正有希望的变革是将人性置于美好的关系（制度）之中，让人性之恶得到规避，人性之善得到弘扬。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3418&rangeEnd=3484",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3418&rangeEnd=3484"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_4_2652-2695",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2652-2695",
      "markText": "真正伟大的革命，不在于摆脱自己身上的枷锁，翻身做主人，而在于让这个国家从此不生产奴隶。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2652&rangeEnd=2695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2652&rangeEnd=2695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_6761-6806",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6761-6806",
      "markText": "在这些时光中，我建立起对多岩石的草地、广阔的田野、大自然的简单之美以及清晰的地平线的热爱。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6761&rangeEnd=6806",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6761&rangeEnd=6806"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_31471-31509",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "31471-31509",
      "markText": "他们教导我们，最好的思想是英国思想，最好的政府是英国政府，最好的人是英国人。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31471&rangeEnd=31509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31471&rangeEnd=31509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_39873-39915",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "39873-39915",
      "markText": "作为一个学生，我发现许多青年人虽然天资聪明，但却没有充分发挥其天赋的自律能力和韧劲。",
      "totalCount": 209,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=663215&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=39873&rangeEnd=39915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/53832d205a1eaf5384ce2fb?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=39873&rangeEnd=39915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "663215_8_51362-51435",
